  "description": "SURVIVE THE APOCALYPSE: Scavenge for supplies, hunt for food, and build shelter in a world overrun by zombies.\n\nEXPLORE MASSIVE LEVELS: Travel by air, land, and sea while discovering hidden secrets and NPCs to help and trade with.\n\nBUILD YOUR HOME: Fortify your base before heading back out to retrieve airdrops, scout deadzones, and battle hordes of supernatural undead.\n\nCOOPERATE OR FIGHT: Team up with friendly players to arrest the bandits, or face-off in intense PvP raids.\n\nTRULY FREE-TO-PLAY: No pay-to-win mechanics, only cosmetic items to further customize your character.\n\nENDLESS CREATIVITY: Create, share, and experience custom maps and mods through the Steam Workshop.\n\nSOURCE CODE: From new features to total conversions, you can rebuild the game with source code and project files available on GitHub.",
